Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.55,0:01:40.84,Default,Cray,0000,0000,0000,,What are you so angry about?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.20,0:01:45.03,Default,Doge,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.16,0:01:47.79,Default,Doge,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, mage!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.25,0:01:52.09,Default,Cray,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry for getting in \Nthe way of your experiment,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.09,0:01:55.13,Default,Cray,0000,0000,0000,,but humans are a dime a dozen \Nas far as you're concerned.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.15,0:01:57.66,Default,Cray,0000,0000,0000,,I thought they were worthless to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.66,0:02:01.63,Default,Cray,0000,0000,0000,,You can just take a quick look around \Nand snatch one right up. Easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.90,0:02:02.63,Default,Cray,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.43,0:02:07.85,Default,Cray,0000,0000,0000,,How rude! I was still talking.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.93,0:02:16.51,Default,Doge,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.39,0:02:22.61,Default,Doge,0000,0000,0000,,Isabelle...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.79,0:02:37.01,Magus-Internal/narrator,Cheesy,0000,0000,0000,,Where am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.16,0:02:47.38,Default,Doge,0000,0000,0000,,Isabelle, did they tease you again?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.90,0:02:49.52,Magus-Internal/narrator,Cheesy,0000,0000,0000,,It's that man's voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.70,0:02:53.19,Default,Cheesy,0000,0000,0000,,This is the appearance that God gave me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.65,0:02:57.69,Default,Cheesy,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like I can help that \Nmy hair is carrot-colored,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.69,0:03:00.32,Default,Cheesy,0000,0000,0000,,or that my eyes are the color of weeds.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.18,0:03:03.52,Magus-Internal/narrator,Doge,0000,0000,0000,,I love you no matter what you look like.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.15,0:03:05.55,Magus-Internal/narrator,Doge,0000,0000,0000,,Cheer up.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.55,0:03:06.96,Magus-Internal/narrator,Doge,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see....
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.14,0:03:09.15,Default,Cheesy,0000,0000,0000,,Ulysse?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.42,0:03:18.96,Default,Cheesy,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, Ulysse!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.17,0:03:22.06,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Isabelle!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.06,0:03:23.39,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,What happened, Isabelle?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.39,0:03:25.26,Default,B,0000,0000,0000,,A child got hit by a carriage!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.26,0:03:26.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.88,0:03:29.80,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,I saw them chasing after Isabelle!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.80,0:03:31.71,Default,C,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's not our fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.71,0:03:32.97,Default,C,0000,0000,0000,,She ran into the street herself!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.94,0:03:36.81,Magus-Internal/narrator,Doge,0000,0000,0000,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.13,0:03:38.11,Magus-Internal/narrator,Doge,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.56,0:03:40.24,Magus-Internal/narrator,Doge,0000,0000,0000,,When is Isabelle waking up?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.63,0:03:42.42,Magus-Internal/narrator,Doge,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't heard her voice in a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.86,0:03:43.85,Magus-Internal/narrator,Doge,0000,0000,0000,,Isabelle.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.22,0:03:45.00,Magus-Internal/narrator,Doge,0000,0000,0000,,Isabelle!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.65,0:03:46.67,Magus-Internal/narrator,Doge,0000,0000,0000,,Isabelle!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.57,0:03:54.11,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Ulysse, Isabelle is gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.80,0:03:57.58,Magus-Internal/narrator,Doge,0000,0000,0000,,She's just sleeping.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.56,0:04:00.16,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,We're going home.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.98,0:04:02.16,Magus-Internal/narrator,Doge,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.16,0:04:03.74,Magus-Internal/narrator,Doge,0000,0000,0000,,No, Father.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.74,0:04:05.30,Magus-Internal/narrator,Doge,0000,0000,0000,,I'm waiting here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.00,0:04:09.66,Magus-Internal/narrator,Doge,0000,0000,0000,,She's going to be lonely \Nif she wakes up alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.92,0:04:10.86,Magus-Internal/narrator,Doge,0000,0000,0000,,Always.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.13,0:04:12.18,Magus-Internal/narrator,Doge,0000,0000,0000,,Forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.51,0:04:34.63,Default,Cheesy,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.02,0:04:36.85,Default,Cheesy,0000,0000,0000,,I woke up, didn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.27,0:04:43.23,Default,Doge,0000,0000,0000,,Chise...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.07,0:04:48.06,Default,Cray,0000,0000,0000,,Elias.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.02,0:05:13.46,Default,Cray,0000,0000,0000,,Aww... Her materials cost\Nquite a bit, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.46,0:05:17.26,Default,Cray,0000,0000,0000,,Corpses aren't free, nor is \Nmanaging the containers.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.88,0:05:20.31,Default,Elias,0000,0000,0000,,Cartaphilus.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.35,0:05:28.27,Default,Cray,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you dare call me by that name.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.60,0:05:37.02,Default,Cray,0000,0000,0000,,You're just a monster that \Nfound a human body.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.16,0:05:42.31,Default,Cheesy,0000,0000,0000,,Elias!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.29,0:05:52.09,Default,Scars,0000,0000,0000,,A freak calling another a freak, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.19,0:05:54.11,Default,Scars,0000,0000,0000,,What a joke.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.63,0:06:02.74,Default,Scars,0000,0000,0000,,I've put a spell on the bullet \Nto stop regeneration.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.34,0:06:05.73,Default,Elias,0000,0000,0000,,Chise, you're alive...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.73,0:06:07.19,Default,Scars,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like it works.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.67,0:06:08.98,Default,Cheesy,0000,0000,0000,,I'm in a bit...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.45,0:06:12.42,Default,Cheesy,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'm in a lot of pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.42,0:06:13.67,Default,Cheesy,0000,0000,0000,,But I made it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.11,0:06:16.50,Default,Elias,0000,0000,0000,,I'm surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.50,0:06:18.96,Default,Cheesy,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a little surprised, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.34,0:06:27.91,Default,Elias,0000,0000,0000,,Chise, am I not terrifying in this form?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.91,0:06:29.57,Default,Elias,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to turn back, so let go.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.60,0:06:34.03,Default,Cheesy,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.77,0:06:38.01,Default,Cheesy,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think you could get through \Nthe door being that tall.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.01,0:06:40.20,Default,Cheesy,0000,0000,0000,,You should probably turn back.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.76,0:06:47.61,Default,Elias,0000,0000,0000,,You're right...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.37,0:06:57.60,Default,Elias,0000,0000,0000,,Silky would be furious with\Nme if I broke the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.00,0:07:01.26,Default,Cheesy,0000,0000,0000,,I'd apologize with you even if she was.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.83,0:07:05.81,Default,Elias,0000,0000,0000,,That's reassuring.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.99,0:07:15.37,Magus-Internal/narrator,,0000,0000,0000,,This girl has strange taste.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.39,0:07:16.53,Default,Yellow,0000,0000,0000,,Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.88,0:07:17.69,Default,Scars,0000,0000,0000,,Alice.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.84,0:07:20.16,Default,Yellow,0000,0000,0000,,Master...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.27,0:07:22.49,Default,Scars,0000,0000,0000,,You idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.91,0:07:25.15,Default,Scars,0000,0000,0000,,Don't go darting off like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.15,0:07:28.38,Default,Scars,0000,0000,0000,,I thought about abandoning \Nyou when I saw your letter.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.38,0:07:29.79,Default,Yellow,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.58,0:07:32.62,Default,Scars,0000,0000,0000,,Don't overestimate your own strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.08,0:07:34.39,Default,Scars,0000,0000,0000,,Think about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.39,0:07:35.31,Default,Yellow,0000,0000,0000,,But!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.75,0:07:37.72,Default,Yellow,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.10,0:07:39.79,Default,Yellow,0000,0000,0000,,You wouldn't have...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.22,0:07:45.14,Default,Scars,0000,0000,0000,,You're my apprentice and my bodyguard.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.76,0:07:50.41,Default,Scars,0000,0000,0000,,A bodyguard ought not to \Nleave their master's side.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.68,0:07:52.49,Default,Yellow,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.93,0:07:54.42,Default,Cray,0000,0000,0000,,You're awful.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.24,0:07:58.97,Default,Cray,0000,0000,0000,,The brain's complicated.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.97,0:08:01.80,Default,Cray,0000,0000,0000,,It takes a lot of work to fix.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.80,0:08:02.92,Default,Scars,0000,0000,0000,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.34,0:08:07.58,Default,Cray,0000,0000,0000,,I just want that dog because \Nhe'd make a good subject.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.97,0:08:11.25,Default,Scars,0000,0000,0000,,Sorcerers don't step into mage territory.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.75,0:08:13.76,Default,Scars,0000,0000,0000,,That was a tacit agreement.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.17,0:08:16.29,Default,Scars,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you go after the fairies?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.74,0:08:19.81,Default,Cray,0000,0000,0000,,Because it seems fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.79,0:08:27.15,Default,Cray,0000,0000,0000,,I could make something interesting \Nif I used a fairy for a chimera.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.63,0:08:31.18,Default,Cray,0000,0000,0000,,But fairy curses are a pain to deal with.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.18,0:08:33.48,Default,Cray,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I put a collar on that sorcerer.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.78,0:08:35.82,Default,Scars,0000,0000,0000,,You monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.81,0:08:42.59,Default,Cray,0000,0000,0000,,I don't need a dog if it \Ncan't even run my errands.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.29,0:08:47.46,Default,Doge,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.46,0:08:51.34,Default,Doge,0000,0000,0000,,that...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.40,0:08:54.60,Default,Doge,0000,0000,0000,,Isabelle?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.50,0:08:59.87,Default,Cheesy,0000,0000,0000,,That isn't your Isabelle.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.69,0:09:03.54,Default,Cheesy,0000,0000,0000,,I've seen you before.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.15,0:09:07.60,Default,Cheesy,0000,0000,0000,,You deceived Matthew in \NUlthar and killed Mina.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.21,0:09:09.89,Default,Cray,0000,0000,0000,,Ulthar?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.89,0:09:12.45,Default,Cray,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, the cat experiment.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.12,0:09:17.62,Default,Cray,0000,0000,0000,,I think I could get some decent \Nresults if I tried it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.20,0:09:19.38,Default,Cray,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.46,0:09:22.43,Default,Elias,0000,0000,0000,,Chise.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.15,0:09:27.39,Default,Cheesy,0000,0000,0000,,You won't have him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.95,0:09:36.56,Default,Cheesy,0000,0000,0000,,I absolutely won't let you have him!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.31,0:09:42.40,Default,Cray,0000,0000,0000,,What an annoying brat.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.15,0:09:51.77,Default,Doge,0000,0000,0000,,Chise...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.06,0:10:01.31,Magus-Flashback,Cheesy,0000,0000,0000,,Anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.31,0:10:02.32,Magus-Flashback,Elias,0000,0000,0000,,Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.32,0:10:07.54,Magus-Flashback,Elias,0000,0000,0000,,Truth be told, you can \Ndo anything with magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.08,0:10:10.46,Magus-Flashback,Elias,0000,0000,0000,,You can turn rocks into gold,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.46,0:10:16.38,Magus-Flashback,Elias,0000,0000,0000,,make fish swim through the sky, \Nkeep harvests from ever rotting.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.89,0:10:21.19,Magus-Internal/narrator,Cheesy,0000,0000,0000,,His words fly through my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.75,0:10:27.56,Magus-Flashback,Elias,0000,0000,0000,,But... that's something that must not be done.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.75,0:10:31.51,Default,Cheesy,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let you have him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.22,0:10:35.38,Default,Cray,0000,0000,0000,,You're pretty knowledgeable for a kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.38,0:10:36.71,Default,Cray,0000,0000,0000,,Tarantula hawks.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.71,0:10:37.77,Default,Cray,0000,0000,0000,,They prey on spiders.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.24,0:10:40.91,Default,Cray,0000,0000,0000,,But being so small,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.37,0:10:44.45,Default,Cray,0000,0000,0000,,they're just going to get eaten.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.53,0:10:50.49,Default,Elias,0000,0000,0000,,Chise, stop this!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.49,0:10:51.89,Default,Elias,0000,0000,0000,,Your body is...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.96,0:10:54.19,Default,Doge,0000,0000,0000,,Mage!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.19,0:10:56.23,Default,Elias,0000,0000,0000,,She just ate a little of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.50,0:10:58.49,Default,Elias,0000,0000,0000,,Chise!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.18,0:11:08.10,Default,Elias,0000,0000,0000,,Chise!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.36,0:11:10.86,Default,Elias,0000,0000,0000,,Chise, you mustn't do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.86,0:11:14.18,Default,Elias,0000,0000,0000,,We must not twist the rules of this world!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.60,0:11:17.56,Default,Darth Yubaba,0000,0000,0000,,Horse and Hattock!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.05,0:11:27.30,Default,Cray,0000,0000,0000,,A fairy spell, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.73,0:11:29.28,Default,Cray,0000,0000,0000,,Not bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.93,0:11:37.21,Magus-Internal/narrator,Cray,0000,0000,0000,,Why did I want that, again?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.72,0:11:39.50,Magus-Internal/narrator,Cray,0000,0000,0000,,To make a chimera.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.50,0:11:41.76,Magus-Internal/narrator,Cray,0000,0000,0000,,Why did I want to make \Na chimera in the first place?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.17,0:11:43.33,Magus-Internal/narrator,Cray,0000,0000,0000,,For what purpose?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.12,0:11:46.85,Default,Cray,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.46,0:11:50.58,Default,Cray,0000,0000,0000,,Now, go find him with your strings.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.50,0:11:56.72,Default,Darth Yubaba,0000,0000,0000,,That wretch won't come looking for us here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.98,0:11:59.06,Default,Elias,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Blue Flame.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.06,0:12:00.90,Default,Darth Yubaba,0000,0000,0000,,The Thorn of Shadows?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.90,0:12:03.15,Default,Darth Yubaba,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it, you've brought so \Nmuch trouble with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.15,0:12:04.99,Default,Elias,0000,0000,0000,,Buy you don't hate it, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.99,0:12:06.06,Default,Darth Yubaba,0000,0000,0000,,Not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.06,0:12:07.56,Default,Yellow,0000,0000,0000,,Get off my head!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.56,0:12:09.16,Default,Elias,0000,0000,0000,,He's a Will-o'-the-Wisp.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.00,0:12:14.83,Default,Elias,0000,0000,0000,,A blue flame fairy that lives in forests \Nand cemeteries, confusing passers-by.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.84,0:12:16.22,Default,Darth Yubaba,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say my name!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.22,0:12:17.61,Default,Darth Yubaba,0000,0000,0000,,That's rude!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.61,0:12:18.63,Default,Elias,0000,0000,0000,,Fine, fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.31,0:12:26.91,Magus-Internal/narrator,Cheesy,0000,0000,0000,,My blood's racing through my body.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.49,0:12:30.62,Default,Elias,0000,0000,0000,,Chise, calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.91,0:12:32.17,Default,Elias,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.48,0:12:34.68,Default,Cheesy,0000,0000,0000,,Elias.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.87,0:12:35.79,Default,Cheesy,0000,0000,0000,,Elias.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.79,0:12:36.72,Default,Cheesy,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.86,0:12:37.91,Default,Cheesy,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.16,0:12:39.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't listen to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.90,0:12:41.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.02,0:12:42.71,Default,Elias,0000,0000,0000,,Be careful from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.08,0:12:44.26,Default,Elias,0000,0000,0000,,That's good enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.71,0:12:55.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chise!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.56,0:13:01.86,Magus-Internal/narrator,,0000,0000,0000,,It feels like my blood's going \Nto overflow and explode.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.54,0:13:04.42,Default,Darth Yubaba,0000,0000,0000,,You're a Sleigh Beggy, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.42,0:13:05.57,Default,Darth Yubaba,0000,0000,0000,,You're so weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.57,0:13:06.80,Default,Darth Yubaba,0000,0000,0000,,Poor thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.19,0:13:09.39,Default,Darth Yubaba,0000,0000,0000,,Take my coal.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.39,0:13:11.26,Default,Darth Yubaba,0000,0000,0000,,You'll feel a little better.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.90,0:13:17.23,Magus-Internal/narrator,Cheesy,0000,0000,0000,,It's warm.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.23,0:13:20.70,Default,Darth Yubaba,0000,0000,0000,,You're finally awake, you sleepy dog.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.70,0:13:21.68,Default,Doge,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not a dog!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.68,0:13:22.36,Default,Doge,0000,0000,0000,,I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.39,0:13:26.20,Default,Darth Yubaba,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be crazy, you dumb dog.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.20,0:13:29.20,Default,Darth Yubaba,0000,0000,0000,,You're neither human, nor an ordinary dog.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.20,0:13:30.90,Default,Darth Yubaba,0000,0000,0000,,Are you still not awake?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.90,0:13:32.38,Default,Darth Yubaba,0000,0000,0000,,Grow up, puppy,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.38,0:13:34.77,Default,Darth Yubaba,0000,0000,0000,,and stop depending on dead people!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.37,0:13:40.75,Default,Darth Yubaba,0000,0000,0000,,Quit whining and go back to \Nyour useful form, church grim!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.58,0:13:49.03,Default,Darth Yubaba,0000,0000,0000,,Your job is to chase the grave \Nrobbers' asses to the gates of Hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.97,0:13:52.17,Default,Darth Yubaba,0000,0000,0000,,You're a black dog.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.91,0:13:55.96,Magus-Internal/narrator,Doge,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.53,0:13:57.76,Magus-Internal/narrator,Doge,0000,0000,0000,,That's what it was.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.30,0:14:00.67,Magus-Internal/narrator,Doge,0000,0000,0000,,I get it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.78,0:14:06.91,Magus-Internal/narrator,Doge,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how long I wait, \Nmy sister won't come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.48,0:14:18.72,Default,Doge,0000,0000,0000,,Chise, will you take me with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.32,0:14:21.00,Default,Doge,0000,0000,0000,,I'll give you my all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.03,0:14:25.42,Default,Darth Yubaba,0000,0000,0000,,You're one thick-headed dog!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.42,0:14:30.31,Default,Darth Yubaba,0000,0000,0000,,Sleigh Beggy or not, we can't be the \Nones to ask a human to make a pact!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.27,0:14:32.44,Default,Cheesy,0000,0000,0000,,A pact?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.71,0:14:35.38,Default,Elias,0000,0000,0000,,He's requesting to become your familiar.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.38,0:14:40.11,Default,Elias,0000,0000,0000,,The ultimate promise, that you would \Nshare everything with one another.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.52,0:14:43.93,Default,Elias,0000,0000,0000,,Your senses, your emotions, even your time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.04,0:14:46.14,Default,Cheesy,0000,0000,0000,,Time?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.87,0:14:49.16,Default,Elias,0000,0000,0000,,If you die, he dies.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.63,0:14:50.45,Default,Cheesy,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.25,0:14:52.27,Default,Doge,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.72,0:14:54.85,Default,Doge,0000,0000,0000,,I've seen inside you, so I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.15,0:15:04.62,Default,Cheesy,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you need to wait for Isabelle?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.46,0:15:09.84,Default,Cray,0000,0000,0000,,There you guys are.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.41,0:15:11.31,Default,Scars,0000,0000,0000,,Cartaphilus!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.21,0:15:16.07,Default,Cray,0000,0000,0000,,I told you not to call me that!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.49,0:15:31.02,Default,Cray,0000,0000,0000,,You're so mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.40,0:15:34.66,Default,Cray,0000,0000,0000,,I'd gotten used to that arm. How inconvenient.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.95,0:15:37.36,Default,Cray,0000,0000,0000,,I won't give your arm back.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.70,0:15:41.87,Default,Scars,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want an arm that's been \Nused as an ingredient for a freak.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.28,0:15:45.13,Default,Cray,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, he's taken on a dog's form.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.13,0:15:46.37,Default,Cray,0000,0000,0000,,That makes him an easier target.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.37,0:15:47.82,Default,Doge,0000,0000,0000,,Please, Chise.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.82,0:15:50.20,Magus-Flashback-internal,,0000,0000,0000,,If you die, he dies.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.20,0:15:52.21,Default,Doge,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want him to take me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.21,0:15:53.50,Default,Doge,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.81,0:15:55.65,Default,Doge,0000,0000,0000,,I'd rather be your...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.48,0:16:00.62,Default,Cheesy,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.80,0:16:06.29,Default,Cheesy,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to be alone anymore, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.74,0:16:21.52,Default,Doge,0000,0000,0000,,Continue after me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.49,0:16:26.12,Default,Doge,0000,0000,0000,,Tie now the silver thread.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.03,0:16:37.19,Default,Cheesy,0000,0000,0000,,Tie now the roots of our veins.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.17,0:16:41.57,Default,Doge,0000,0000,0000,,The holly, so that we may not be separated.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.24,0:16:46.40,Default,Cheesy,0000,0000,0000,,The ivy, so that we may not come apart.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.91,0:16:51.11,Default,Cheesy,0000,0000,0000,,Tie to the yew tree seven times.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.92,0:16:55.34,Default,Cheesy,0000,0000,0000,,Until the day the snake spits out its tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.63,0:17:10.31,Default,Doge,0000,0000,0000,,Chise, give me a new name.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.65,0:17:14.30,Default,Doge,0000,0000,0000,,Take me by your side.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.97,0:17:19.90,Default,Cheesy,0000,0000,0000,,Come,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.33,0:17:22.28,Default,Cheesy,0000,0000,0000,,Ruth.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.72,0:18:09.02,Default,Cray,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, dear.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.02,0:18:10.91,Default,Cray,0000,0000,0000,,He woke up from his dream of being human.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.39,0:18:17.90,Default,Doge,0000,0000,0000,,Good night, Isabelle.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.08,0:18:30.63,Default,Doge,0000,0000,0000,,Wait for me until my time with her is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.63,0:18:39.86,Default,Cray,0000,0000,0000,,Too bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.86,0:18:41.65,Default,Cray,0000,0000,0000,,So you belong to her now, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.75,0:18:45.39,Default,Cray,0000,0000,0000,,Undoing a pact is such a pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.39,0:18:47.68,Default,Scars,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you back off, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.68,0:18:48.56,Default,Cray,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.56,0:18:49.80,Default,Cray,0000,0000,0000,,I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.59,0:18:52.55,Default,Cray,0000,0000,0000,,What's with that look?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.55,0:18:56.42,Default,Cray,0000,0000,0000,,You learn to give up quickly \Nwhen you live for a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.21,0:18:59.71,Default,Scars,0000,0000,0000,,What is the purpose that drives you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.92,0:19:03.16,Default,Cray,0000,0000,0000,,To live without suffering.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.56,0:19:08.24,Default,Cray,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sick of rotting away until an end \Nthat I don't even know will come.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.37,0:19:10.38,Default,Cray,0000,0000,0000,,It hurts.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.38,0:19:11.25,Default,Cray,0000,0000,0000,,It's painful.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.49,0:19:12.39,Default,Cray,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.39,0:19:14.63,Default,Cray,0000,0000,0000,,But why is my body like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.99,0:19:18.74,Default,Scars,0000,0000,0000,,You don't mind making others \Nsuffer for your sake?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.52,0:19:20.65,Default,Cray,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.99,0:19:24.36,Default,Cray,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that how living things are?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.01,0:19:29.15,Default,Elias,0000,0000,0000,,If that's what you think, you're \Nneither human nor beast.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.61,0:19:33.65,Default,Elias,0000,0000,0000,,You're nothing but a monster in \Nhuman form, Cartaphilus.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.99,0:19:39.56,Default,Cray,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Joseph, little boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.85,0:19:43.91,Default,Cray,0000,0000,0000,,See you around.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.48,0:19:50.64,Default,Scars,0000,0000,0000,,He's like a natural disaster.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.25,0:19:54.93,Default,Elias,0000,0000,0000,,At least disasters are knowable.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.56,0:19:57.00,Default,Elias,0000,0000,0000,,Cartaphilus...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.62,0:20:04.24,Default,Scars,0000,0000,0000,,It's said that the Son of God cursed\Nhim so that he can never die.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.86,0:20:11.01,Default,Scars,0000,0000,0000,,He's a monster that roams aimlessly, \Ndriven only to satiate his curiosity.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.56,0:20:15.46,Default,Elias,0000,0000,0000,,And what happened was the result of \Nbeing chosen by that monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.51,0:20:18.97,Default,Elias,0000,0000,0000,,Just why?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.81,0:20:22.98,Default,Scars,0000,0000,0000,,My head may have flown if I'd refused.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.98,0:20:24.33,Default,Scars,0000,0000,0000,,I had no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.85,0:20:26.08,Default,Elias,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.03,0:20:28.25,Default,Scars,0000,0000,0000,,You.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.68,0:20:30.44,Default,Scars,0000,0000,0000,,Have you met him before?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.90,0:20:31.96,Default,Elias,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Him{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.96,0:20:33.49,Default,Elias,0000,0000,0000,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.27,0:20:35.18,Default,Scars,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.33,0:20:38.39,Default,Elias,0000,0000,0000,,Be careful on your way home.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.39,0:20:40.83,Default,Scars,0000,0000,0000,,I don't need you to worry for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.01,0:20:42.98,Default,Scars,0000,0000,0000,,We're going.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.44,0:20:44.33,Default,Yellow,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.37,0:20:49.67,Default,Darth Yubaba,0000,0000,0000,,Now, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.67,0:20:52.78,Default,Darth Yubaba,0000,0000,0000,,I have to send them off.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.30,0:21:14.20,Default,Elias,0000,0000,0000,,You sure are a hard worker.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.70,0:21:18.71,Default,Darth Yubaba,0000,0000,0000,,My job is to send the living to the swamp.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.97,0:21:23.71,Default,Darth Yubaba,0000,0000,0000,,But my job is also to see the dead \Noff to the gates to the other side.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.11,0:21:30.54,Default,Darth Yubaba,0000,0000,0000,,This one is artificial, but being so, \Nit'll bear an artificial soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.91,0:21:40.30,Default,Darth Yubaba,0000,0000,0000,,See you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.14,0:21:47.67,Default,Elias,0000,0000,0000,,Well, we'd better head home, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.15,0:21:50.71,Default,Elias,0000,0000,0000,,I can explain things to you tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.20,0:21:52.48,Default,Elias,0000,0000,0000,,You must be tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.71,0:21:53.69,Default,Cheesy,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.43,0:21:56.54,Default,Elias,0000,0000,0000,,Your scolding will come \Nwhen we get home, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.54,0:21:57.53,Default,Cheesy,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.36,0:21:59.45,Default,Cheesy,0000,0000,0000,,Ruth.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.28,0:22:04.09,Default,Cheesy,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go home together, Ruth.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.23,0:22:08.14,Default,Doge,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.00,0:22:15.43,Default,Doge,0000,0000,0000,,From now on, where you go \Nhome is where I go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.90,0:23:57.58,Default,Cheesy,0000,0000,0000,,A new friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.58,0:24:00.27,Default,Cheesy,0000,0000,0000,,A brief, peaceful rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.27,0:24:05.55,Default,Cheesy,0000,0000,0000,,The girl steps into a beautiful rose garden, \Nher mind still burdened by her troubles.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.24,0:24:09.57,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Speak of me, and I'll eat you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.57,0:24:11.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
